rComments: She's really interesting in class and I like how she relates organization behaviors to scientific theories. Funny personality and fairly balanced marker. Lots of memorization, however, and that is the only way to get an easy A.

She's a great prof! You'll know she loves teaching and she's very accommodating to students. Her explanations and examples are very helpful. She's a bit of a strict marker but as long as you put the right amount of effort to your work, you should do just fine. = )
